data.description: Beautifully updated and move-in ready 2-story situated on a generous sized lot that backs up to green space for added privacy. Designed for easy living and perfect for entertaining with main floor formal living and dining rooms, family room, open concept kitchen with oversized eating space, bedroom/flex space and utility room. Upstairs features a spacious primary with 5-piece ensuite bath and huge closet, 2 bedrooms and full bath. Enjoy the fully fenced backyard with new Trex deck making it the perfect outdoor living space. Attached 2-car garage. Additional features include new roof, HVAC, appliances, tile and hardwood flooring, and much, much more. This home has everything you need. Welcome to your dream home!
